{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04031/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04031"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:40:31"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman poses in a ballgown for a photoshoot with crew members surrounding the set."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04031","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04031"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1/0deb9486-71f4-462d-9b1d-0993f00fb352","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:12:31.596Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>During the photoshoot, the dialogue is divorced from the scenes and layered over, generating a strange effect. We see what the characters are discussing but at a temporal remove. This play with diegetic and non-diegetic sound conveys the sense of excitement surrounding the photoshoot for Alma.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:82.69179004037684,91.00942126514141,282.9609690444146,196.393001345895"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1/02622e19-8af2-4105-bffb-d672a4427a0c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:12:57.963Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Photographer Laura Hynd was invited to produce a project documenting the film’s lavish costumes and design. She visited several locations, taking shots of fittings and the costume and art departments. However, during this photoshoot, she was asked to <em>be</em> in the film as a photographer (Padley, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW15268830 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.anothermag.com/design-living/10514/behind-the-scenes-of-a-new-film-about-1950s-british-couture\"><u>Behind the Scenes</u></a>”). Hynd’s work can be seen in the book <em>The Women of Woodcock </em>(2018).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04031/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:899.2732166890983,385.59892328398394,310.0942126514133,574.9663526244952"}}}]}]}]}